vclaim: A photograph shows David Chipman, U.S. President Joe Biden's ATF nominee, posing before the charred ruins of the Branch Davidian compound in Waco in 1993.
title: No, This Is Not a Photo of Biden’s ATF Nominee David Chipman at Waco
subtitle: A photograph from the deadly siege on the Branch Davidian compound has been shared with misleading information.
author: Bethania Palma
